            <title>[KAFKA-6622] GroupMetadataManager.loadGroupsAndOffsets decompresses record batch needlessly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-6622</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
